== Bloggin' ==

Bloggin' is a Minimal Ruby on Rails powered Blogging platform. Bloggin' is powered by mongodb and mongoid.
Comments are driven by disqus and app wide settings are controlled by a single YAML file.


== Configuration ==

To personalize Bloggin' simply edit configuration.yml located at config/configuration.yml.
Once you have personalized Bloggin' deploy to heroku(after configuring mongohq of course).
Or deploy to your choice of VPS.


== Upcoming Features ==

* Asset Uploads
* 100% Test Coverage
* Easy Theme Switcher